<section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-medium text-slate-900 mb-6">How we make you the obvious choice.</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Three pillars to dominate your local market. We handle the heavy lifting, you handle the new customers.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <!-- Pillar 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-slate-900">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-900 mb-3">Top of Google Maps</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Show up first when locals search for your service. If you're not in the top 3, you're invisible.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4">Full profile optimisation, directory listings, and ongoing Maps ranking management.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pillar 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-slate-900">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" /></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-900 mb-3">First Page of Google</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Your business on Page 1 — not your competitors, not some directory. You. Organic traffic that comes to you every day.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4">SEO-optimised pages targeting the exact words your customers type. Suburb expansion as rankings grow.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pillar 3 -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-slate-900">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" /></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-slate-900 mb-3">5-Star Review Engine</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Build a wall of 5-star reviews — without lifting a finger. More reviews means more trust means more calls.</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 border-t border-slate-100 pt-4">Automated review requests after every job. Happy customers go to Google. Concerns go to a private form.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="mt-16 text-center">
    <a
      href="https://calendar.app.google/ceK9b3Jr3KGD9cCs5"
      target="_blank"
      class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-white bg-slate-900 rounded-full hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
    >
      Book a Free Strategy Session
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
